HEADWORD: Monograph
<hw>Mon"o*graph</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Mono-</ets>
+ <ets>-graph</ets>.]</ety> <def>A written account or description of a
single thing, or class of things; a special treatise on a particular
subject of limited range.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

